---
title: Chopped Salad Gyro Wrap with Beyond Meat® and Chunky Fries
description: This classic gyro wrap is as tasty as it is colourful! Our shawarma spice blend is smoky, sweet and oh so delicious. Paired with juicy tomatoes, crisp cucumber and drizzled with tangy chili-yogurt sauce, dinner tonight hits all the high notes!
